Package: edfkmeans
Type: Package
Title: Degrees of freedom and model selection for k-means clustering
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-07-27
Author: David Hofmeyr <dhofmeyr@sun.ac.za> [aut, cre]
Maintainer: David Hofmeyr <dhofmeyr@sun.ac.za>
Description: Uses a generalisation of Stein's lemma to approximate the effective degrees of freedom
for k-means. This is then used within BIC to select the number of clusters present in the data.
License: GPL-3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.16)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
